You unleash the bolt swiftly, watching as it flies true. It strikes with a resolute impact, a final, disabling blow that sends the formidable beast crashing to the ground, subdued by your skill and strategy.

The immediate threat has passed, and the forest seems to exhale with you. What will you do now in the aftermath of this tense encounter?","stateChanges":{"encounterEnded":{"outcome":"victory"},"npcChanges":[{"npcId":"npc-01KM35F016ZR4DPK3FQ0B19FVD","field":"hp","oldValue":20,"newValue":0}]}}

