{"narrativeText":"Keeping well clear of the boars' wandering path, you edge your way around the clearing to the stone structure nestled amidst the vegetation. As you draw closer, the shrine reveals itself—a weathered relic of ancient craftsmanship, its surface adorned with faded runes similar to those on the amulet.

Though time and elements have worn away much of its detail, there's a palpable aura of past significance here. The atmosphere is serene, a stark contrast to the earlier tension.

